.TH LIGHTNING-NODE-PAY-COUNT-SKEWNESS 1
.SH NAME
lightning-node-pay-count-skewness \- compute pay_count_skewness via listpays
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning node-pay-count-skewness
.SH DESCRIPTION
Queries the node via \fBlightning-cli listpays\fR and computes pay_count_skewness.
